Speakers: Ant Pegg & Bradley Maglinger

Language: English

The open community continues to strengthen and drive public and private commitment, where the MapQuest team has renewed vision. Focused on supporting OSM contributions of open data, knowledge and technologies, MapQuest representatives will share key learnings from our work with OSM over the last 4 years, providing open services to the community. We'll also share our plans are for continuing that relationship, adding more definition and support in the near term.
